= Facebook Connect Demo Application

== Description

This is a demo application for Facebook Connect on Rails.

== Requirement

sudo gem install facebooker (optional)

== Contain plugin

Restful Authentication
http://github.com/technoweenie/restful-authentication/tree

Facebooker
http://github.com/mmangino/facebooker/tree/master


